node.text:
By @moe.hoteit: “𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐮𝐧𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐡 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐩𝐞𝐚𝐤 𝐩𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐫𝐨𝐮𝐠𝐡 𝐚 𝐮𝐧𝐢𝐪𝐮𝐞 𝐛𝐮𝐜𝐤𝐞𝐭 𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐭 𝐚𝐝𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐟𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐚?⁣⠀
⁣⠀
We have designed a Life-Changing Experience, an 𝐀𝐝𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐏𝐮𝐫𝐩𝐨𝐬𝐞, to challenge you in every possible way and push you towards your greatness, all while doing good for others.⠀
⠀
Here’s what you get by joining:⠀
⠀
✔️Challenge yourself & journey up the tallest mountain in Africa: Mt.Kilimanjaro with change-makers like yourself. Designed with your safety as our top priority with proper acclimatization time. Our team of professionals aims to make this a wonderful experience for you in every way.
⁣⠀⠀
✔️⁣Experience one of the 7 natural wonders of Africa & observe dense wildlife at the Ngorongoro Crater where mankind supposedly started.
⠀
✔️Make an Impact on children's lives in underserved communities in Africa & be their voice. We've partnered with the SlumCode Group, a non-profit, and 10% of your fee will be donated to build schools for youth leadership development in those poor communities.⠀
⠀
✔️Receive Top Notch Guidance & Coaching throughout the whole process.⠀
⁣⠀⠀
✔️Customized (at minimum) 2 months body & mind training program. Training starts no later than October 1st.⠀
⠀
𝘈𝘯𝘥 𝘜𝘭𝘵𝘪𝘮𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘭𝘺, 𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘤𝘩 𝘠𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘗𝘦𝘢𝘬 𝘗𝘰𝘵𝘦𝘯𝘵𝘪𝘢𝘭!⁣⠀
⠀
This is not your typical adventure. This is your legacy in the making. ⠀
⠀
Join us 𝐃𝐞𝐜 𝟖𝐭𝐡-𝟏𝟕𝐭𝐡, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟏 on this life-changing adventure.⁣⠀
⁣⠀
Registration closes 𝐎𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟏𝐬𝐭, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟏.⁣⠀
⁣⠀
LIMITED SPOTS LEFT.⠀
⁣⠀
𝐂𝐋𝐈𝐂𝐊 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊 in @moe.hoteit Bio for detailed information about the adventure.

P.S: Make sure to also follow @moe.hoteit for transformational content & adventure retreats.
